into a space opera situation. I wanted to do some more relevant comment. You haven't asked a question on this, but I'll 
give you the answer anyway. I'd just like to think that I'm on Earth for some purpose other than just to feed my face. I want

19:24.188 --> 19:29.674
to do something and try to leave the universe a better place than it was when I came into it. If there's anything in my power 
