19:39.333 --> 19:50.832
to write, in the guise of fiction, to write material that people will read and become better persons or get ideas that 
they wouldn't have. I've had some comments from fans saying that after reading some of my novels, they're thinking of

19:50.852 --> 19:57.282
the Split Infinity series, They've decided that honesty is the best policy. Now they admire honesty. Well, that 
pleases me. That's the kind of thing I want to do. If a person was planning to be dishonest and he reads one of my novels and

20:04.647 --> 20:13.581
then he decides that he really would rather be honest, I believe in honesty. I want to encourage it. I think there should 
