20:24.478 --> 20:25.800
money at it, yes. But while I'm making the money, I also want to do something that, well, when I die, I can look back and say I 
have done something useful in the world. So this is why I'm not satisfied just to write and get paid for it and not to worry

20:34.379 --> 20:41.813
about the theme or the content. I want to do something that I can be satisfied with, that I can be proud of, and that will 
help people. You have alluded several times to the fact that your fans asked you to do this and your fans said that. I take

20:55.019 --> 21:01.329
it that you either correspond with fans or you do get quite a bit of fan mail and that you are responsive to it. Yes. It's a 
