31:54.437 --> 31:57.581
from the ordinary card playing deck. I bought a deck of my own, tried spreading out a reading, and it was amazing. I should 
say, I don't believe in the supernatural. I have absolutely no belief in anything supernatural. So I try these things as

32:09.520 --> 32:11.362
an experiment. I said, OK, let's ask a question and lay out according to the formula and see what the cards say. And the 
cards answered my questions. And this got to me. I said, if I don't believe in the supernatural, how can the supernatural

32:22.947 --> 32:27.973
agency work for me? And again, by the time I finished figuring that out, I had a novel on hand. I think I did figure out how it 
